Subject: [PATCH] Apply file patches


diff --git a/net/minecraft/nbt/NbtOps.java b/net/minecraft/nbt/NbtOps.java
index a6d88f43aade9885145f11efb8be0c9ffcb832b6..ae7a7390ba376508f925ee33a3b8390b8da23ccd 100644
--- a/net/minecraft/nbt/NbtOps.java
